node.text:
We are always looking for eco-friendly ways to enjoy the beautiful Pacific Northwest. We are excited to introduce you to @soulcommunityplanet and the #EveryStayDoesGood program! Through charitable partnerships, every stay at one of their hotels does good for you, good for local communities, and good for the planet. Experience a new level of fulfillment while you explore the Oregon High Desert at @scpredmond and the Oregon Coast at @scpdepoebay.
.
Please help us send a warm welcome and a big thank you to @soulcommunityplanet for creating such beautiful and impactful places for us to enjoy our region. Follow along their accounts and keep them in mind for your next adventure. #pnwonderland
